{#- One-line, secret-free summary of an AWS profile: region, named profile,
    role ARN, whitelisted plugin fields, and the credential mode. Secret fields
    (secret_access_key, session_token) are stripped by datus before rendering;
    access_key_id is checked for presence only and never emitted. -#}
{%- macro aws_summary(cfg, extra_fields=[]) -%}
{%- set parts = [] -%}
{%- if cfg.get("region") %}{% set _ = parts.append("region=" ~ cfg.get("region")) %}{% endif -%}
{%- if cfg.get("profile") %}{% set _ = parts.append("aws_profile=" ~ cfg.get("profile")) %}{% endif -%}
{%- if cfg.get("role_arn") %}{% set _ = parts.append("role=" ~ cfg.get("role_arn")) %}{% endif -%}
{%- for field in extra_fields -%}
{%- if cfg.get(field) %}{% set _ = parts.append(field ~ "=" ~ cfg.get(field)) %}{% endif -%}
{%- endfor -%}
{%- if cfg.get("access_key_id") %}{% set _ = parts.append("creds=keys") -%}
{%- elif cfg.get("role_arn") %}{% set _ = parts.append("creds=assume-role") -%}
{%- else %}{% set _ = parts.append("creds=chain") %}{% endif -%}
{{- parts | join(", ") -}}
{%- endmacro -%}
{% if profiles %}
## EMR
Operate existing Amazon EMR (on EC2) clusters through `datus emr <group> <subcommand>` (`--profile <env>` before the group).
Groups: `clusters` (list, describe, instances) and `steps` (list, describe, add [--wait], cancel, logs). This drives EXISTING clusters — cluster provisioning/termination is out of scope (use IaC). `steps add` submits billed work; `steps logs` reads step stdout/stderr from the configured S3 log_uri. Add `-o json` for machine-readable output. Consult the `emr` skill before composing non-trivial commands.
Environments ({{ profiles | length }}):
{% for name, cfg in profiles.items() -%}
- {{ name }}: {{ aws_summary(cfg, ["cluster_id"]) }}
{% endfor -%}
{% else %}
## EMR (installed, not configured)
The `datus emr` CLI is installed but has no environment configured.
{% if config_mutable %}
Run the `emr-setup` skill to configure one.
{% else %}
Configuration is managed by the deployment administrator — tell the user to contact them.
{% endif %}
{% endif %}
